            ("p", "Influencer marketing lives or dies on one decision: who you partner with. Pick well and a single post can drive a wave of real business; pick poorly and you've paid for a vanity metric that produced nothing. Follower count is the flashiest number and the least reliable, so here's the vetting process we actually use to choose creators."),
